#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-kig.1.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "An interactive geometry program by &kde;"
msgstr "Interaktivni geometrijski program &kde;"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-kig.1.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kig</command> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-c, --convert-to-"
"native</option> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-o, --outfile "
"<replaceable>filename</replaceable></option> </group> </group> <arg choice="
"\"opt\">options</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kig</command> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-c, --convert-to-"
"native</option> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-o, --outfile <replaceable>ime "
"datoteke</replaceable></option> </group> </group> <arg choice=\"opt"
"\">možnosti</arg>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kig.1.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kig.1.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kig; is an application for interactive geometry. It is intended to serve "
"two purposes:"
msgstr "&kig; je aplikacija za interaktivno geometrijo. Služi dvema namenoma:"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kig.1.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To allow students to interactively explore mathematical figures and concepts "
"using the computer;"
msgstr ""
"Študentom omogočiti interaktivno raziskovanje matematičnih oblik in "
"konceptov z uporabo računalnika;"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kig.1.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To serve as a WYSIWYG tool for drawing mathematical figures and including "
"them in other documents."
msgstr ""
"Služiti kot orodje WYSIWYG za risanje matematičnih oblik in njihovo "
"vključitev v druge dokumente."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kig.1.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this program you can do geometry on a computer just like you would on a "
"blackboard in a classroom. However the program allows you to move and change "
"parts of a geometrical drawing so that you can see how other parts change as "
"a result."
msgstr ""
"S tem programom lahko izvajate geometrijo na računalniku tako kot na tabli v "
"učilnici. Vendar vam program omogoča premikanje in spreminjanje delov "
"geometrijske risbe, tako da lahko vidite, kako se posledično spreminjajo "
"drugi deli."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kig.1.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kig; supports loci and user-defined macros. It also imports and exports "
"both to and from foreign file formats including <application>Cabri</"
"application>, <application>Dr. Geo</application>, &kgeo;, <application>KSeg</"
"application> and <application>XFig</application>."
msgstr ""
"&kig; podpira lokuse in uporabniško definirane makre. Prav tako uvaža in "
"izvaža v in iz tujih formatov datotek, vključno z <application>Cabri</"
"application>, <application>Dr. Geo</application>, &kgeo;, <application>KSeg</"
"application> in <application>XFig</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kig.1.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "This application is part of the official &kde; edutainment module."
msgstr "Ta aplikacija je del uradne aplikacije &kde; izobraževalni modul."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kig.1.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Možnosti"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kig.1.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "-c, --convert-to-native"
msgstr "-c, --convert-to-native"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kig.1.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do not show a &GUI;. Instead convert the specified file to native &kig; "
"format. The native &kig; file will be written to standard output unless "
"<option>--outfile</option> is passed."
msgstr ""
"Ne prikaži &GUI;. Namesto tega pretvori podano datoteko v izvorni &kig; "
"format. Izvorni &kig; datoteka bo zapisana v standardni izhod, razen če je "
"podana <option>--outfile</option>."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kig.1.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "-o, --outfile <replaceable>filename</replaceable>"
msgstr "-o, --outfile <replaceable>filename</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kig.1.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Used with <option>--convert-to-native</option> to specify where to save the "
"newly created &kig; file. Not specifying this option, or providing a "
"filename of <filename>-</filename> will output the file to standard output."
msgstr ""
"Uporablja se z <option>--convert-to-native</option> za določitev, kam naj se "
"shrani novo ustvarjena mapa &kig;. Če te možnosti ne določite ali podate ime "
"datoteke <filename>-</filename>, bo datoteka prikazana v standardnem izhodu."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kig.1.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "See Also"
msgstr "Poglejte tudi"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kig.1.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More detailed user documentation is available from <ulink url=\"help:/kig"
"\">help:/kig</ulink> (either enter this &URL; into &konqueror;, or run "
"<userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> <parameter>help:/kig</parameter></"
"userinput>)."
msgstr ""
"Podrobnejša uporabniška dokumentacija je na voljo na <ulink url=\"help:/kig"
"\">help:/kig</ulink> (vnesite ta &URL; v &konqueror; ali zaženite "
"<userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> <parameter>help:/kig</parameter></"
"userinput>)."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kig.1.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also further information available at the <ulink url=\"https://edu."
"kde.org/kig/\">&kde; Education website</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Dodatne informacije so na voljo tudi na <ulink url=\"https://edu.kde.org/kig/"
"\">&kde; Izobraževalnem spletnem mestu</ulink>."

